<p>RPX is a service that makes it easy for users to sign in or register on your site using an existing account from Google, Yahoo, AOL, Facebook, MySpace, Twitter and others without having to use a new password. By reducing the barriers for users, it can increase site registration and participation. For more information visit <a onclick="window.open(this.href,'_blank');return false;" href="https://rpxnow.com/">http://rpxnow.com</a>.</p>
<p>If you already have an RPX account for this site from rpxnow.com, you should enter the API key and then click the Setup RPX button.</p>
<p>If you don't yet have an account, leave all fields blank and click the Setup RPX button. You will be redirected to RPXnow.com and after completing the account setup, RPXnow.com will redirect you back here and the settings will be updated automatically.</p>